# overworld.pal — Background palettes for overworld levels
# 4 sub-palettes × 4 colors = 16 NES color IDs
# Color 0 of each sub-palette is the universal background ($21 = sky blue)

# Sub-palette 0: Sky / Clouds / Text
21 30 10 00

# Sub-palette 1: Ground / Bricks
21 27 17 07

# Sub-palette 2: Pipes / Bushes / Vegetation
21 2A 1A 09

# Sub-palette 3: Coins / ? Blocks / Special
21 28 18 08
